Subject: User not syncing
Description: A user who used to appear in our admin panel via AD Sync is missing. A manual sync did not resolve the issue and we are unable to add him manually. His name is Kris Hall, username is KDHall, and email is kris.hall@mortonbank.com.
What_We_Know__c: Dusing the remote session I changed the DB flags for the reported user for "deleted", "is_active", and "is_super_admin" to "0", "1", "1".
Next_Steps__c: We are waiting for the customer to confirm with the user that the epp UI console is now working.
Solution_Comment__c:
During the remote session, I updated the flags in the database for the reported user who was marked as deleted and not active.
The customer has confirmed that the user is able to access the EPP UI.
